---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="CV" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">CV / Resume</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Well rounded and passionate full stack Software Creator with the ability to adapt and learn
    whatever skills are needed to create the best product possible for the customer.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Senior Software Engineer"
      subtitle="Mayo Clinic, Rochester, MN"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 mt-1 space-y-1">
        <li>Implemented POC AI Agents to investigate and validate AI platforms for alignment to Enterprise Architecture.</li>
        <li>Refined documentation for decision enabler for AI Platforms.</li>
        <li>Developed AI based backend APIs using Python.</li>
        <li>Pod lead for local and overseas React UI dev team.</li>
        <li>User Experience designer and architect.</li>
        <li>Maintained and enhanced multiple web apps.</li>
        <li>Assisted in architecting Microsoft Power Platform application.</li>
        <li>Maintained / reimplemented Python ETL scripts.</li>
        <li>Lead initiatives to mature product development lifecycle for multiple teams.</li>
        <li>Lifecycle management in ADO, Apigee, Azure, and GCP.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Tech Specialist 1"
      subtitle="Mayo Clinic, Rochester, MN"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 mt-1 space-y-1">
        <li>Architected new Java / Angular applications.</li>
        <li>Built reusable "shell" application used for starting new Angular frontends.</li>
        <li>Created shareable library for managing interaction with Informatica via Apigee.</li>
        <li>Migrated multiple applications from Akana to Apigee.</li>
        <li>Assisted others with setting up new applications in Azure.</li>
        <li>Mentored multiple coworkers.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Senior Analyst Programmer"
      subtitle="Mayo Clinic, Rochester, MN"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 mt-1 space-y-1">
        <li>Implemented multiple applications from gathering requirements to production deployment.</li>
        <li>Developed example applications in Angular and C# for use as a base for future applications to expedite development by less experienced engineers.</li>
        <li>Maintained and enhanced various C#, Java, JavaScript/TypeScript, and Python applications.</li>
        <li>Developed and maintained SAS macro applications for ETL jobs between disparate databases.</li>
        <li>Supported and extended SAP Crystal Reports and SAP Business Object environments for government compliance.</li>
        <li>Team subject matter expert for Java, SQL, Angular, Bash, JavaScript, TypeScript, Azure DevOps, and Akana.</li>
        <li>Team proponent for standardization of new technologies.</li>
        <li>Member of Java steering committee.</li>
        <li>Investigated, designed, and implemented changes needed for FDA CFR 21 Part 11 compliance.</li>
        <li>Full lifecycle implementation of GUIs for medical image analysis using Python and MATLAB, including a next-generation MRI image quality control interface.</li>
        <li>Implemented work management system using the Trac open source project.</li>
        <li>Documented standard operating procedures for audit compliance.</li>
        <li>Reorganized, simplified, and standardized source code control to allow multiple instances to run concurrently with simple install procedures using SVN, Bash, Git, and Mercurial.</li>
        <li>Managed and contributed to open source project pyXnat.</li>
        <li>Optimized SQL queries for significant performance improvement.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Senior Software Engineer"
      subtitle="Vision Solutions, Rochester, MN"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4 mt-1 space-y-1">
        <li>Lead the move to "Web 2.0" and Ajax.</li>
        <li>Implemented standards, tools, and documentation for creating portlets that matched company strategy.</li>
        <li>Developed theme for, and customized, Jetspeed 2.2 Portal for strategic interface platform.</li>
        <li>Developed example portlets using selected technologies for other departments to build upon.</li>
        <li>Maintained, designed, and extended Spring-based web application.</li>
        <li>Re-architected database schemas to improve performance.</li>
        <li>Audited previously designed web applications, made recommendations, and implemented performance improvements.</li>
        <li>Created, maintained, and presented training materials for multiple projects.</li>
        <li>Participated in user interaction testing and helped improve requirements and usability.</li>
        <li>Developed a cross-platform rich client interface with Swing GUI toolkit.</li>
        <li>Developed reusable Swing components for use in multiple products.</li>
        <li>Provided direct support to customers on software product problems.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor of Science in Computer Science (Cum Laude)"
      subtitle="Winona State University, Winona, MN"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="font-semibold mb-2">Languages</div>
    <ul class="list-disc md:columns-4 columns-2 mx-6 mb-6">
      <li>TypeScript / JavaScript</li>
      <li>HTML / CSS</li>
      <li>Python</li>
      <li>Bash / Shell</li>
      <li>Java</li>
      <li>C#</li>
      <li>C / C++ / Objective-C</li>
      <li>Swift</li>
      <li>SAS</li>
      <li>R</li>
      <li>Matlab</li>
      <li>SQL</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="font-semibold mb-2">Frameworks &amp; Libraries</div>
    <ul class="list-disc md:columns-4 columns-2 mx-6 mb-6">
      <li>React</li>
      <li>Astro</li>
      <li>Vue</li>
      <li>Angular</li>
      <li>Redux</li>
      <li>Pandas / NumPy</li>
      <li>AI / LangChain</li>
      <li>WxWidgets</li>
      <li>Gtk</li>
      <li>OAuth</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="font-semibold mb-2">Tools &amp; Platforms</div>
    <ul class="list-disc md:columns-4 columns-2 mx-6 mb-6">
      <li>Docker</li>
      <li>Node</li>
      <li>Bun</li>
      <li>Claude Code / OpenCode</li>
      <li>Azure DevOps</li>
      <li>Google Cloud</li>
      <li>SharePoint</li>
      <li>Crystal Reports</li>
      <li>SAP BOXI / BODS</li>
      <li>PostgreSQL</li>
      <li>MongoDB</li>
      <li>Firebase</li>
      <li>BigQuery</li>
      <li>Git / SVN</li>
      <li>Trac</li>
      <li>Balsamiq Mockups</li>
      <li>Figma</li>
      <li>Lucid Chart</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
